headline.main: 'PLYMOUTH PARTY' AIDS ENGLISH CITY; Sir Gerald Campbell a Patron of a Benefit Dinner Dance for War Sufferers MANY DINNERS ARE GIVEN Mrs. Gerald E. Cave Chairman of Fete Under Sponsorship of Bundles for Britain

lead_paragraph: Under the distinguished patronage of Sir Gerald Campbell, British Minister to the United States, and Lady Campbell, a benefit dinner dance entitled "Party for Plymouth" was given last night at Le Coq Rouge under the sponsorship of Bundles for Britain, Inc.
